The '''Digsite workmen''' can be found in and around the [[Digsite]], as well as carrying rocks to the [[Varrock Museum]]. They can also be [[Pickpocketing|pickpocketed]], giving 10.4 [[Thieving]] [[experience]] if successful.

They play an important role in [[The Dig Site]] [[Quests|quest]] as one may steal an [[animal skull]] from them. Also, players who come to work at the Digsite without the necessary tools can pickpocket the workmen and eventually gain most of the items needed, although this can take some time.

==Pickpocketing info==
{{Thieving info
|level = 25
|xp = 10.4
|type = Pickpocket
|tool = None
}}

Notable about these workmen is that pickpocketing takes roughly twice as long to execute, compared to other pickpocketable NPCs. Interestingly, workmen give [[coins]] when pickpocketed, instead of [[coin pouch]]es.

